text: The Ahmadi Governorate (Arabic: محافظة الأحمدي) is the second-most populated governorate of Kuwait. It is home to several major oil companies. == Districts == The Ahmadi Governorate is made up of 14 different districts. * Abu Halifa * Al-Ahmadi * Egaila * Daher * Fahaheel * Fintas * Hadyia * Jaber Al-Ali * Mahboula * Mangaf * Riqqa * Subahiya * Sabah Al-Ahmad Sea City * Wafra == References == Category:Governorates of Kuwait
title: Ahmadi Governorate
